data.description: Your country home awaits!  This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath rambler is situated on a 0.97-acre lot with stunning wooded views and was constructed in 2022. The front of the house features stone accents and black gutters, with additional yard space on both sides of the home. The large front yard has an extended gravel driveway that leads to the attached garage and a huge 27’x27’ newly built carport. The backyard is huge and has a lovely tree line that provides a calming, peaceful view you can enjoy year after year.  Inside the home, you are greeted with magnificent luxury vinyl plank flooring and upgraded crown molding that extends throughout the main living area and down the bedroom hallway. The open floor plan makes indoor entertaining a simplified task. You will absolutely love prepping meals in this incredible gourmet kitchen with marvelous quartz countertop space that includes a center island and breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, a pull faucet, loads of two-tone cabinet storage with modern pulls, and a custom tile backsplash for that touch of extra character. The spacious dining area has access to the rear and lighting with a rustic charm.  At the end of the hall, the large Owner’s Suite boasts a tray ceiling, two separate closets, and a fantastic ensuite with an oversized shower, double vanity sinks, and ceramic tiling. The full hall bath also displays ceramic tiling, and the remaining two spacious bedrooms have elevated cable jacks and outlets to mount your TVs with a clean look.  Come and enjoy peaceful country living on a one-level almost newly built home and be minutes away from everything! I-95's Thornburg exit 118 is justa 7-minute drive and Cosner's Corner is less than 15 min away!
